Janet Egyir (amụrụ na 7 Mee 1992 na Sekondi-Takoradi) bụ onye Ghana na-agba bọọlụ mba ụwa nke na-agba dịka onye na-agbachitere Afturelding / Fram na Iceland
Ọ bụ otu n'ime ndị otu na 2014 African Women's Championship. N'afọ 2018, a mara ya ikpe dịka onye egwuregwu kachasị mma nke asọmpi ahụ na 2018 WAFU Women's Cup
Na Mee 2016 ọ bịanyere aka na Víkingur Ólafsvík na Iceland.
